{
  "texts": [
    "Additionally, llama-2-13b-chat-hf was not accurate in providing the output activity in the required format.",
    "As we described in Section 3.3.4, the system prompt instructs the system to enclose the most likely activity within curly braces.",
    "While gpt-3.5-turbo-0125 always complied, llama-2-13b-chat-hf often did not adhere to this instruction.",
    "This required us to find ad-hoc solutions to extract activity labels when the output format was different.",
    "Furthermore, llama-2-13b-chat-hf tended to output activity labels not even semantically close to the predefined activity sets, such as 'moving around the house'."
  ]
}